meta {
  name: Support · Update ticket
  type: http
  seq: 4
}

put {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/v2.2/support/tickets/:id
  body: json
  auth: inherit
}

params:path {
  id: <id>
}

headers {
  Content-Type: application/json
}

body:json {
{
  "status": "active"
}
}

docs {
**Update ticket status**
Updates the status of a ticket. Customers can only update their own tickets.

Note: `:id` here is the support ticket **sequence integer** (e.g. `1015`), not a phone number.

OperationId: `ticketsPut`
}
